original_title: Go, Diego, Go!: The Great Dinosaur Rescue
overview: While visiting a dinosaur museum, Alicia tells Diego, Dora and Baby Jaguar a story about a young Maiasaura who got separated from her family herd. To help the lost reptile reunite with her family, it'll take the combined efforts of an animal rescuer, a great explorer and a dinosaur expert. Transporting themselves back in time to the Cretaceous period to help Maia, Diego, Dora, Alicia and even Baby Jaguar may just fill the bill!
tagline: Jump back to the time of the Dinosaurs for Diego's BIGGEST animal rescue yet!
title: Go, Diego, Go!: The Great Dinosaur Rescue
